ance isn’t self-contained. See also ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorPaths\/isSelfContained()","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/editorpaths\/getselfcontainedfile()","title":"getSelfContainedFile()","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getSelfContainedFile"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorPaths\/getSelfContainedFile()"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/EditorPaths/isSelfContained()":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Returns ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":" if the editor is marked as self-contained, "},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" otherwise. When self-contained mode is enabled, user configuration, data and cache files are saved in an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"editor_data\/"},{"type":"text","text":" folder next to the editor binary. This makes portable usage easier and ensures the Godot editor minimizes file writes outside its own folder. Self-contained mode is not available for exported projects."}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/editorpaths\/isselfcontained()","title":"isSelfContained()","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"isSelfContained","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/EditorPaths\/isSelfContained()"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/EditorPaths":{"title":"EditorPaths","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Editor-only singleton that returns paths to various OS-specific data folders and files."}],"kind":"symb